{"parentUuid":"d6138f5e-92ea-45a7-ace1-84bdf994522a","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01Hx4sdiZk5UzxAHDi6M14i6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PostgreSQLでのUNIQUE制約の書き方は2つです：\n\n**カラムレベル**（1カラムのみ）\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE example (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  email VARCHAR UNIQUE\n);\n```\n\n**テーブルレベル**（1カラムまたは複数カラム）\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE example (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  email VARCHAR,\n  UNIQUE(email)\n);\n```\n\n**制約に名前をつける場合**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE example (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  email VARCHAR,\n  CONSTRAINT uc_email UNIQUE(email)\n);\n```\n\n複数のカラムでユニークにする場合：\n```sql\nUNIQUE(column1, column2)\n```\n\nプロジェクトのマイグレーションルールによると、CHECKは制約はアプリケーション側で担保することになってますが、UNIQUEについては特に制限がないので、DBレベルで制約を入れるなら上記の形式で大丈夫です。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30076,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":654,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30076,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJhinZq6386LCRFAsShy","type":"assistant","uuid":"db53e324-5cf6-46a4-ad86-cc3ca73db293","timestamp":"2026-03-22T19:52:51.284Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b7c6001a-f145-4c61-8443-6b080eca5019","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
