{"parentUuid":"43a820d1-9c49-4102-90e1-98d1ce5652de","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01BCPanGuVzJETUjtMVvZNsT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1227,"cache_read_input_tokens":30076,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1227},"output_tokens":6,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJidxHTVb7re2sJPXL5B","type":"assistant","uuid":"612dc0ab-3c4b-49af-93bc-8bf77bddd438","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:04:50.393Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b7c6001a-f145-4c61-8443-6b080eca5019","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"612dc0ab-3c4b-49af-93bc-8bf77bddd438","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01BCPanGuVzJETUjtMVvZNsT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"いいえ、PostgreSQL は **自動的にはインデックスを作成しません**。\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE courses (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id INT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id)\n  -- ↑ このだけではインデックスが作られない\n);\n```\n\n外部キー参照元のカラムにインデックスを使いたい場合は、明示的に作成が必要です：\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE courses (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id INT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id)\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX idx_courses_user_id ON courses(user_id);\n```\n\n**ポイント：**\n- **参照元（courses.user_id）** にインデックスを張ると良い\n  - 外部キー制約の確認が高速化\n  - JOINやフィルタリングが高速化\n- **参照先（users.id）** は PRIMARY KEY なので既にインデックスがある\n\nマイグレーションファイルに入れるなら：\n\n```sql\n-- テーブル作成\nCREATE TABLE courses (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id INT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),\n  _created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now(),\n  _updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now()\n);\n\n-- インデックス作成\nCREATE INDEX idx_courses_user_id ON courses(user_id);\n```"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1227,"cache_read_input_tokens":30076,"output_tokens":681,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1227,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJidxHTVb7re2sJPXL5B","type":"assistant","uuid":"a9ba5bcc-e42e-4aa5-bba8-c38eb26ffa91","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:04:52.693Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b7c6001a-f145-4c61-8443-6b080eca5019","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
