{"parentUuid":"5e38b70e-6f67-41c7-9ddf-1d0b53792163","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01Fc6gXUkryNE3B3KATMam9D","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":710,"cache_read_input_tokens":31303,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":710},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJif5tddEC2ceWypzimw","type":"assistant","uuid":"ddaa6bfa-1a64-4511-8901-5e77a5d75393","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:05:05.854Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b7c6001a-f145-4c61-8443-6b080eca5019","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"ddaa6bfa-1a64-4511-8901-5e77a5d75393","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01Fc6gXUkryNE3B3KATMam9D","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**必須ではありませんが、ほとんどの場合あった方がいいです。**\n\n**インデックスがあると便利な場合：**\n- 参照元のカラムで `WHERE` 条件に使う（例：`WHERE user_id = 1`）\n- `JOIN` で頻繁に結合する\n- 外部キー制約チェックが高速化（削除時など）\n\n**インデックスなしでもいい場合：**\n- そのカラムでフィルタリング・結合をほぼしない\n- テーブルが非常に小さい\n- 書き込みが極めて多く、インデックス更新のコストが問題\n\n---\n\n**実務的には：**\n- `user_id` みたいに、ユーザーごとのデータを取得する際に頻繁に使うカラムなら → **インデックスを貼る**\n- 参照するだけで検索に使わないなら → **貼らなくてもいい**\n\nこのプロジェクトであれば `courses.user_id` は「ユーザーの全コースを取得」みたいに使うはずなので、**インデックスを貼った方がいい** と思います。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":710,"cache_read_input_tokens":31303,"output_tokens":739,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":710,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJif5tddEC2ceWypzimw","type":"assistant","uuid":"e2847cad-9030-4b32-baeb-9f535170195e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:05:08.536Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"b7c6001a-f145-4c61-8443-6b080eca5019","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
